creator: Ergomotion
descriptionHtml: Dawn House APP focuses on user convenience, rich functions and sleep health data. The APP interface is simple and intuitive. After connecting to a smart device, the user can view real-time data and control the adjustable base. With the function of imitating the remote control attached to the adjustable base, the sensor can detect the user's sleep state.
descriptionShort: Dawn House focuses on user convenience, rich functions and sleep health data.

title: Dawn House

creator: Ergomotion
descriptionHtml: Accessible from your smartphone or tablet, your sleep and health reports are easily visible in the Dawn House app. View real-time data, and daily, weekly, monthly and yearly metrics for your sleep levels, heart rate, heart rate variability and more. Share health reports with loved ones, customize your bed settings and sync your bed with your smart phone devices all for a more independent and vibrant life.
descriptionShort: Dawn House can make your life more independent and energetic.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
1. Years are added to sleep report, Out of bed module is added, and sleep report chart is optimized.
2. Add 12 hour system and 24 hour system.
3. Add Health Connect function.
4. Self diagnosis adds diagnostic report sharing function.
5. Optimize sleep report sharing.
